Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving an emergency signal, \Nthey landed on Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a strange island divided
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into two parts; the Burning \NLands and the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To rescue Nami and the others \Nwho are held captive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's group headed to the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they were unaware that some
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,former acquaintances were also on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here - to my vacation home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Chase-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Warlord! Trafalgar Law!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar! I know you're a Warlord but \Nwe need you to ask you to step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know somebody else is here on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:13.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,INSIDE OF DR. VEGAPUNK'S FORMER \NLABORATORY NAMI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:13.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you said "We are not sick \Nanymore" earlier, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of sickness did you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of you look sick to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But they \Ntold us that we were sick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'd get better in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get better in a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And people who were asked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to treat me by my dad and \Nmom took me to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means your parents \Nsent you to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:06:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, those people told \Nme that out of the blue in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,front of my house and took me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they didn't want my \Ndad and mom to get infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I couldn't even say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened to you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un-huh.\N--Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It seems they were kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some strangers took them here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without letting them see their parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could only mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're really very sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If any of you can't run, \NI'll carry you on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all look fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are! The Master has been treating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Master!\N--Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's been over a year, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, why don't you examine them later?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! This door is locked! \NWe have nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They are coming!\N--What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more! Hi-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open. Wachaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So strong!\N--You became very powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was cool, Racoon-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not a racoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you look like one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing! Chopper, \Ncan I borrow your fur?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it outside? Or is it a freezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark. I can barely see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you're from a Winter Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a path? It's \Ntoo dark and I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see it! There's a door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! It's not a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis! I don't like this place! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's wrong, kids?\N--Let's go! They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first got here, I \Nwalked through this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means it'll lead us to the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really cold but hang on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you look around...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something in the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This path scares me because there \Nare frozen people all around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead bodies in ice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sis, wait! Don't leave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I think I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:50.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,INSIDE OF THE LABORATORY - \NBISCUIT ROOM SANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:50.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you blocked their path already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! I just felt \NNami-san's inner scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she wants to tell me that she loves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're half sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there was a mythical \Ncreature like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother to think about them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get the whole picture first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go save Nami-san now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Leave me here! I want to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boy was not among those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be other rooms so I'll stay and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even move on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave you here, we would \Nfeel like we're abandoning you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not a great feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm here to rescue my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't irritate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just ask me to find your body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna owe anything to pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't ask you even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-However, if you want to look for my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a severed-head! \NDon't be so arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna use violence against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna beg a thug for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna feel better by \Nsmashing a helpless severed-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you took him out of the room, \Nyou already gave in to him, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so stupid to be moved \Nby his determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm not even capable of \Nfighting back if someone hits me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can carry me if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We'll settle this once \Nyou get your body back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You show no mercy even on \Na severed-head like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better watch my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nami found the way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really... itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:11.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PUNK HAZARD ISLAND - THE \NMIDDLE LAKE LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you, intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he sliced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Zoro-kun! I have to compliment you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I got Leg-maro too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He cut the shell in half?!\N--Damn samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't clear the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they're dumb, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Leg-maro Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing something again-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leg-maro has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He repelled them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with his body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Devil Fruit eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna shoot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never learn. I'll \Nbe counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're aiming at the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna try to sink the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We have two Devil \NFruit eaters on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let them fall into the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rot in hell, Devil Fruit eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get behind an iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you rowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fruit eaters can't fight in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink to your death, Devil Fruit eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:59.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A SNOW-CAPPED MOUNTAIN \NNEAR THE LABORATORY BROOK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross! So gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly attacking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to get attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind of strong too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear something in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have ears though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice! I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forget I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't have eyes anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MAIN ENTRANCE OF THE LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? My name is Monkey D. Luffy! I'm \Ngonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You picked up too fast and said too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold... Is this the Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not the Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My colleagues are getting \Ncut one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai are gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody please help me! I'm on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Punk Hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the island and \Nthe fact he said "It's cold."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is almost no doubt that this \Nman sent the signal from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Straw Hat Luffy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the incident involving the Roswalds,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Celestial Dragon family, \Nhappened on Sabaody 2 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, Straw Hat and you fought together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And during the War of the Best...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put Straw Hat-ya on my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna help him get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of him for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Akainu was after Straw Hat,  you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...helped him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you Navy people are good at \Nforging those emergency signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it wasn't a trap that we set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know anything so there's \Nnothing more to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us see inside the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my vacation home now. I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me - a pirate staying \Non an island you people abandoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Straw Hat comes, I'll \Nchop his head off for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all you have to say, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So scary! Those frozen people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it with this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look! There's a door! We can get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is somebody else in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside?! It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got out of the building! I can go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see my dad and mom again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear the way, clear the way, Super the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run over you if you stand in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I avoid running over flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of sweet - Franky Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Here we go, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats?! Children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big racoon, a woman in bikini \Nin the winter, giant kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a robot, and a severed-head...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dreaming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tank treads!\N--Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Awesome!\N--A tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad roads won't trouble me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the way you shiver \Nin the cold but I don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you to get sick so take my jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he was there at Sabaody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who locked \Nup these children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brute! You can't take them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who this \Nvillainous guy was! Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good! The Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't escape from here! \NLet's look for another exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, kids! Go to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought the Navy to such a place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I thought the Navy were good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go to them, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they look like gangsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lied! You weren't the only one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like I wasn't. I'm also surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, let's catch the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go! Follow Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ouch!\N--Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools... They brought trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's making that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The warship is in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the bottom of the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you leave the island now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I said no one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are no match!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll chop off your hands and feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Smo-yan!
